item.title: CVE-2022-43431|2024-08-03T13:32:58.885Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20compuware%20strobe%20measurement%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Compuware Strobe Measurement Plugin 1.0.1 and earlier does not perform a permission check in an HTTP endpoint, allowing attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins.
